data.description: Welcome to this light and bright one story brick home in the community of Polo Ranch. This home is situated on a  cul-de-sac street with few back neighbors & features an open-concept design with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and 2 car garage. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, breakfast bar & painted 42' white cabinetry. The primary bedroom offers an ensuite with soaking tub, separate shower & a generous walk-in closet. Additional features are large Laundry/Utility room with space for extra refrigerator, mudroom with cubbies and bench. Secondary bedroom are large with double door closets. Outside offers covered patio overlooking a massive private fully fenced yard. Come see this gem!
